      <title>對沖基金巴林頓敦促派拉蒙取消與 Skydance 的談判</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/hedge-fund-barington-urges-paramount-scrap-talks-with-skydance-2024-04-12/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[對沖基金巴林頓資本 (Barington Capital) 週五敦促派拉蒙全球公司 (Paramount Global) 放棄與 Skydance Media 的獨家合併談判，稱如果該公司考慮其他潛在競購者，所有股東都將受益。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/hedge-fund-barington-urges-paramount-scrap-talks-with-skydance-2024-04-12/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 18:53:47 GMT</pubDate>
